message: "If you use this software, please cite it."
title: "AgentTwin: a multi-agent digital-twin testbed for supervisory operating-mode scheduling and residual regulatory control on the Tennessee Eastman Process with a solver-backed safety shield"
abstract: >
  AgentTwin is a reproducible simulation-based digital-twin testbed and
  multi-agent residual-control framework for the Tennessee Eastman Process.
  It couples supervisory operating-mode scheduling, residual SAC regulatory
  control, and a solver-backed QP safety shield.
